burlap.oomdp.statehashing

Class FixedSizeStateHashableStateFactory

  • java.lang.Object
    • burlap.oomdp.statehashing.SimpleHashableStateFactory
      • burlap.oomdp.statehashing.ImmutableStateHashableStateFactory
        • burlap.oomdp.statehashing.FixedSizeStateHashableStateFactory
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    HashableStateFactory

    public class FixedSizeStateHashableStateFactory
extends ImmutableStateHashableStateFactory
    This is a hash factory specifically for FixedSizeImmutableStates. It allows you to set a mask, to only hash a subset of objects or object classes. Because it only works for FixedSizeImmutableStates, it hashes objects specifically in the order there exist in the state. It also iterates staight through when doing the state equality comparison, allowing for significant speedups for certain domains.
    Author:
    brawner
